Geex 1.0 API

Packages 
Package Description
nl.tudelft.context
Main package for the ProgrammingLife context project.
nl.tudelft.context.breadcrumb
Package containing the breadcrumb.
nl.tudelft.context.controller
Package containing all the controllers used in the application.
nl.tudelft.context.controller.graphlist
A package containing the controller to manipulate the current active graph.
nl.tudelft.context.controller.locator
A package containing the controller to locate and interact with the graph locator.
nl.tudelft.context.controller.overlay
A package containing the controllers that use an overlay.
nl.tudelft.context.controller.search
Controller for the NewickSearch.
nl.tudelft.context.drawable
Everything in this package is drawable in JavaFx.
nl.tudelft.context.drawable.graph
Everything drawable used in the Graph view.
nl.tudelft.context.effect
This package is contains visual effects.
nl.tudelft.context.logger
Package containing the logger class and interfaces.
nl.tudelft.context.logger.message
Package containing all Messages and MessageTypes.
nl.tudelft.context.model
This package is the root for all model classes.
nl.tudelft.context.model.annotation
Contains annotations in two different forms.
nl.tudelft.context.model.graph
Package containing all files related to creating a Graph.
nl.tudelft.context.model.graph.filter
This package contains all filters for the main graph view.
nl.tudelft.context.model.newick
Package containing all classes related to creating a Newick tree.
nl.tudelft.context.model.newick.node
Package containing all node classes related to the Newick tree.
nl.tudelft.context.model.newick.selection
Package containing selection classes for double dispatch.
nl.tudelft.context.service
Package containing services for loading files.
nl.tudelft.context.window
A window to be used by the controllers.
nl.tudelft.context.workspace
Package for the workspace.
